articles.title: Travis Kelce spotted back in Las Vegas as fans speculate whether he'll join Taylor Swift in Australia - Page Six
articles.description: The “Anti-Hero” hitmaker has four shows lined up in Sydney before she travels to Singapore to continue her Eras Tour.
articles.content:
Travis Kelce is enjoying some time on the golf course following his Super Bowl win and not in Australia with Taylor Swift.
